name: IndexedConversionOptions

properties.name: colors
properties.description: The number of colors in the palette. Not valid for all palette types.

properties.name: forced
properties.description: The type of colors to force into the color palette.

properties.name: transparency
properties.description: If true, preserves transparent areas of the image during conversion to GIF format.

properties.name: ditherAmount
properties.description: The amount of dither. Valid only when 'dither' = diffusion.

properties.name: preserveExactColors
properties.description: If true, protects colors in the image that contain entries in the color table from being dithered. Valid only when 'dither' = diffusion.

properties.name: matte
properties.description: The color to use to fill anti-aliased edges adjacent to transparent areas of the image. When transparency = false, the matte color is applied to transparent areas.

description: Options for converting an RGB image to an indexed color model.
